</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#1f1f1f"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Kai</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">There's a good idea.  If the GMs had a tool to change these on the fly, or even per player that would help in fixing the overpowered classes - God knows Verant cant fix squat<p>Kai
